<section class="pt-ab-hero">
  <div class="pt-ab-hero__bg">
    <div class="pt-ab-hero__grid"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-ab-hero__content">
    <p class="pt-ab-hero__eye">Our story</p>
    <h1 class="pt-ab-hero__h1">Built on one idea.<br><em>Done right.</em></h1>
    <p class="pt-ab-hero__sub">We didn't set out to build a clothing brand. We set out to build one tee worth keeping.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="pt-ab-stats">
  <div class="pt-ab-stat">
    <span class="pt-ab-stat__num">240</span>
    <span class="pt-ab-stat__lbl">GSM fabric weight</span>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-ab-stat">
    <span class="pt-ab-stat__num">4</span>
    <span class="pt-ab-stat__lbl">Considered colourways</span>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-ab-stat">
    <span class="pt-ab-stat__num">1</span>
    <span class="pt-ab-stat__lbl">Uncompromising standard</span>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="pt-ab-story">
  <div class="pt-ab-story__visual">
    <div class="pt-ab-story__avatar">
      <span class="pt-ab-story__initials">PT</span>
    </div>
    <p class="pt-ab-story__name">Founder, Plain Theory</p>
    <p class="pt-ab-story__role">Designer &amp; Builder</p>
    <p class="pt-ab-story__loc">Delhi NCR · Est. 2025</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-ab-story__content">
    <p class="pt-ab-story__eye">Why we exist</p>
    <h2 class="pt-ab-story__title">We got tired of buying tees that didn't last.</h2>
    <p class="pt-ab-story__para">Every tee we owned either shrank, pilled, or lost its shape within a few months. The ones that felt good were either too expensive to wear daily or too flimsy to justify the price.</p>
    <p class="pt-ab-story__para">So we built one tee worth keeping. 240 GSM combed cotton. Oversized by design. Side-seam construction. Pre-shrunk. No corners cut, no compromises made.</p>
    <p class="pt-ab-story__para">Plain Theory is not a brand trying to be everything. It's one product, done right, for people who buy fewer but better things.</p>
    <p class="pt-ab-story__sig">— Founder, Plain Theory</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pt-ab-values">
  <div class="pt-ab-values__header">
    <p class="pt-ab-eye">What we stand for</p>
    <h2 class="pt-ab-stitle">Three things we refuse to compromise on.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-ab-values__grid">
    <div class="pt-ab-val">
      <span class="pt-ab-val__num">01</span>
      <p class="pt-ab-val__title">Quality over quantity</p>
      <p class="pt-ab-val__body">We make one tee. Not five. Not a new drop every week. One tee, made properly, that you'll still be reaching for two years from now.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-ab-val">
      <span class="pt-ab-val__num">02</span>
      <p class="pt-ab-val__title">Deliberate design</p>
      <p class="pt-ab-val__body">The oversized fit isn't a trend. The drop shoulder isn't decorative. Every design decision has a reason — comfort, drape, and durability.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-ab-val">
      <span class="pt-ab-val__num">03</span>
      <p class="pt-ab-val__title">Honest pricing</p>
      <p class="pt-ab-val__body">₹1,499 for a 240 GSM tee is not expensive. It's the correct price for what this is. We'd rather charge fairly once than cut the fabric to cut the cost.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pt-ab-timeline">
  <div class="pt-ab-values__header">
    <p class="pt-ab-eye">The journey</p>
    <h2 class="pt-ab-stitle">How Plain Theory came to be.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-ab-tl">
    <div class="pt-ab-tl__item">
      <div class="pt-ab-tl__dot"></div>
      <p class="pt-ab-tl__year">The problem</p>
      <p class="pt-ab-tl__text">Kept buying tees that shrank, pilled, or lost their shape. No honest middle ground existed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-ab-tl__item">
      <div class="pt-ab-tl__dot"></div>
      <p class="pt-ab-tl__year">The research</p>
      <p class="pt-ab-tl__text">Sampled dozens of GSM weights. Landed on 240 GSM combed cotton as the only honest answer.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-ab-tl__item">
      <div class="pt-ab-tl__dot"></div>
      <p class="pt-ab-tl__year">The product</p>
      <p class="pt-ab-tl__text">Built one tee. Four colours. Side-seam construction. Woven labels. Pre-shrunk. Nothing extra, nothing missing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-ab-tl__item">
      <div class="pt-ab-tl__dot"></div>
      <p class="pt-ab-tl__year">The launch</p>
      <p class="pt-ab-tl__text">Plain Theory launches in Delhi NCR, 2025. One drop. Four colours. For people who buy fewer, better things.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pt-ab-cta">
  <p class="pt-ab-eye">Ready?</p>
  <h2 class="pt-ab-cta__title">One tee. Four colours.</h2>
  <p class="pt-ab-cta__sub">The original drop is live. Pick yours.</p>
  <div class="pt-ab-cta__chips">
    <div class="pt-ab-chip"><span class="pt-ab-chip__dot" style="background:#1a1a1a"></span>Washed Black</div>
    <div class="pt-ab-chip"><span class="pt-ab-chip__dot" style="background:#E8DCC8"></span>Vintage Cream</div>
    <div class="pt-ab-chip"><span class="pt-ab-chip__dot" style="background:#3D4535"></span>Military Olive</div>
    <div class="pt-ab-chip"><span class="pt-ab-chip__dot" style="background:#4D5562"></span>Storm Slate</div>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-ab-cta__btns">
    <a href="/collections/all" class="pt-ab-cta__btn-p">Shop now — ₹1,499</a>
    <a href="/pages/size-guide" class="pt-ab-cta__btn-s">Size guide</a>
  </div>
</section>

